<p>
    
    We, The Ride You Rent, are committed to protecting the privacy and personal information of our customers. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect the information you provide to us when using our car rental services. By using our services, you agree to the terms and practices described in this Privacy Policy.</P>

    <P>Information We Collect:

    Personal Information: We may collect personal information such as your name, address, email address, phone number, driver's license details, and payment information when you rent a car from us.
    Reservation Information: We collect information about your car rental reservations, including pickup and drop-off locations, rental dates, and any special requests or preferences.
    Usage Information: We may collect information about how you interact with our website or mobile application, including your IP address, device information, browser type, pages visited, and referring website.
    Use of Information:

    Service Delivery: We use the collected information to fulfill your car rental reservations, provide customer support, and deliver the requested services.
    Communication: We may use your contact information to communicate with you regarding your reservations, updates, special offers, and promotional materials. You can opt-out of receiving marketing communications at any time.
    Improving Services: We analyze usage data to enhance and improve our car rental services, website, and user experience.
    Legal Compliance: We may process your information to comply with legal obligations, enforce our terms of service, or protect our rights, property, or safety.
    Data Retention:
    We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

    Data Sharing and Disclosure:

    Service Providers: We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in delivering our car rental services, such as payment processors, insurance providers, and vehicle maintenance companies.
    Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law, court order, or government regulations, or to respond to a legal request or protect our rights, property, or safety.
    Data Security:
    We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please note that no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
</P>
